V 332
define a new BC_WITH_SUB_FLAG_ARGS macro that is just like BC_WITH_FLAG_ARGS providing --with-* flags, but they are --with-sub flags so they will not propagate settings outside of a subconfigure.  this lets us do things like tell libpng to use our libz or a system libz instead of adding duplicate infrastructure to their configure.
END
